TASK_DESCRIPTION=Extend taskmaster-wait.sh stale detection to auto-kill and restart workers stuck >180s. Detection infrastructure exists (90s heartbeat, 60s boot stuck). Gap is enforcement: kill Claude process, relaunch with preserved task context. Add Subtaskmaster-level idle enforcement: kill/restart workers with no tool calls for >120s while BUSY. Depends on state machine and recovery patterns. Research material: .doey/tasks/attachments/task-490-findings.md Area 9.
